2.title: You Can't Live with Them
2.plot: Dark County is a secret hiding in plain sight, existing mostly in our world, but partly somewhere else. The citizens, living in the thirteen townships within the county's borders, know that something is...off in their little corner of the world, but few have every wanted to talk about it, until now. imdb.plot outline: Dark County is a secret hiding in plain sight, existing mostly in our world, but partly somewhere else. The citizens, living in the thirteen townships within the county's borders, know that something is...off in their little corner of the world, but few have every wanted to talk about it, until now. The Dark County Sheriff's Department, after a generation's old tradition of keeping everything that happens in the County quiet, is facing new challenges in this modern world of social media, smart phones and the internet. The old ways, in this new age, would only serve to draw more unwanted scrutiny. Dark County is about secrets, and how far you sometimes have to go to keep them.
